Victor Woolf https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victor_Woolf 0 Victor John Woolf (1911–1975) was an English actor, both on stage and on screen. He worked behind the scenes as well, notably as the stage manager in the 1969 West End production of Mame. Victor_John_Woolf ( 1911 – 1975 ) was an_English_actor , both on stage and on screen .
